numerical algorithms by Pan \\cite{Pan02jsc} and\nSch\\\"onhage \\cite{Sch82}. To our knowledge the presented bounds are the best\nknown for the problem of real root isolation for algorithms based on exact\ncomputations.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 8 Oct 2010 18:54:07 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Tue, 26 Apr 2011 09:17:21 GMT"}],"update_date":"2011-04-27"}
